data.title: Libra Antique Bronze Family In Arches Sculpture Large
data.meta_description: New from Libra is this Antique Bronze Family In Arches Sculpture Large featuring a family of four under four bronze arches.
data.text:
New from Libra is this Antique Bronze Family In Arches Sculpture Large featuring a family of four under four bronze arches.

Libra are well known for their humanist sculptures and this piece is the latest addition to their range.

Finished in antique bronze colour, those who are familiar with Libras sculptures will know that they are quite heavy this particular sculpture weighing in at just over 1.5kg.

For further information about the Libra Antique Bronze Family in Arches Sculpture Small please give our sales team a call.
